1. Volim da putujem, *ali* nemam dovoljno novca. (I like to travel, *but* I don't have enough money.)
2. Ona je pametna, *ali* malo tvrdoglava. (She is smart, *but* a bit stubborn.)
3. Uspela sam da nađem stan, *ali* nije u najboljem kraju grada. (I managed to find an apartment, *but* it's not in the best part of town.)
4. Sviđa mi se ovaj model cipele, *ali* nema moju veličinu. (I like this shoe model, *but* it doesn't come in my size.)
5. Povrće je zdravo, *ali* ne volim ukus karfiola. (Vegetables are healthy, *but* I don't like the taste of cauliflower.)
6. Ne mogu da dođem na vašu proslavu, *ali* hvala na pozivu. (I can't come to your party, *but* thank you for the invitation.)
7. *Ali*, šta se to dogodilo? (But, what happened?) 
8. Nikada nisam bila u Japanu, *ali* planiram da odem jednog dana. (I've never been to Japan, *but* I plan to go one day.) 
9. Moramo da pronađemo rešenje, *ali* nije lako. (We have to find a solution, *but* it's not easy.)
10. Želela sam da idem na koncert, *ali* karte su rasprodate. (I wanted to go to the concert, *but* the tickets are sold out.)